arStrings.szText: You there, yes you! Come now, don't be shy. I need your help, that damned fanatic Theya stole my eyes!
lude, drunk, or a madman. shouts at everyone
She wears them around her neck, and what horrid suffering I've witnessed. Please, no more. There's so much blood... I can't...
You must believe me, I can still see from them. Theya and her flock have grown strong in Nostrava. Please, bring me back my eyes.
